doctype html
html
    include ./head.pug
    body

        h1 API Project: Request Header Parser Microservice

        h3 User Story:
        p I can get the IP address, preferred languages (from header Accept-Language) and system infos (from header User-Agent) for my device.


        section
            div(class="row")
                h3 Example Usage:
                code [base_url]/api/whoami

                h3 Example Output:
                p.
                    {“ipaddress”:”::ffff:159.20.14.100”,”language”:”en-US,en;q=0.5”, “software”:”Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Ubuntu; Linux x86_64; rv:50.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/50.0”}

            div(class="row")
                a(href="/api/whoami") Who am I?
                include ./display.pug

        include ./footer.pug